{"tid":1675903,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳貼「不招待曱甴」告示　譚仔澄清：有人惡意捏造","createTime":"2019-10-26T06:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T07:52:24.000Z","uid":81228,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f41a70aec2460f6801dcc2f9ebe901bc7df05b8","tid":1675903,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191026/_2019102613554080193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191026%2F_2019102613554080193.jpg&h=dd868931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網傳譚仔貼「不招待曱甴」告示。網上圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191026/_2019102614244356055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191026%2F_2019102614244356055.jpg&h=bd5fe029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚仔澄清指告示有人惡意捏造。<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波持續將近四個月，近月有被指抹黑示威者的店舖及中資銀行被破壞。網上流傳一張圖片，指在 觀塘廣場的「譚仔雲南米線」，貼出一張告示寫「本店注重環境衛生，不招待曱甴及不文明人士，不便之處請自省!」，署名為「譚仔雲南米線」，引起討論。<br />\n<br />\n譚仔澄清指，關於網上流傳疑似譚仔告示並非譚仔雲南米線撰寫，網上圖片內容全屬虛構，店內員工亦從未張貼相關告示，相信屬於人惡意捏造，高度重視此問題，保留法律追究的權利。<br />\n<br />\n圖片在Facebook及各個網上討論區流傳，不少網民紛紛到「譚仔雲南米線」fb專頁留言，要求譚仔解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1622265/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%B2%BC-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8B%9B%E5%BE%85%E6%9B%B1%E7%94%B4-%E5%91%8A%E7%A4%BA-%E8%AD%9A%E4%BB%94%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%8D%8F%E9%80%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1622265%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25B2%25BC-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25BE%2585%25E6%259B%25B1%25E7%2594%25B4-%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25A4%25BA-%25E8%25AD%259A%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2583%2